==Description== 

The [[Image:Design456_ExtrudeFace.svg|24px]] [[Design456 ExtrudeFace]] lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Curabitur at felis ut urna auctor pharetra id at nulla. This tool is part of the [https://www.freecad.org/addons.php external workbench] called [[Design456 Workbench|Design456]].

==Usage== 

# Switch to the [[Image:Design456_workbench_icon.svg|24px]] [[Design456 Workbench|Design456]] workbench (install from [[Image:Std_AddonMgr.svg|24px]] [[Std_AddonMgr|Addon Manager]] is necessary, if not previously installed)
# Select a face from a 3D object
# Press the [[Image:Design456_ExtrudeFace.svg|24px]] Extrude Face command. A copy of the face will be created and the command ask you for the length of the extrusion. Later the extruded face will be created on the same direction of the face.

==Limitations==

Works on 3D objects. 

